{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.1","label":"","reference":"Esdras 1:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.036.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.001.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">\u00c9dit de Cyrus. Retour de la captivit\u00e9 de Babylone<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-11: cf. 2 Ch 36:20-23. (J\u00e9 25:11, 12; 29:10-14. \u00c9s 44:26-28; 45:1-13; 49:13-17.) Ro 11:23.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.1.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    La premi\u00e8re ann\u00e9e de Cyrus, roi de Perse, afin que s\u2019accompl\u00eet la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel prononc\u00e9e par la bouche de J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, l\u2019\u00c9ternel r\u00e9veilla l\u2019esprit de Cyrus, roi de Perse, qui fit faire de vive voix et par \u00e9crit cette publication dans tout son royaume:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1","name":"Esdras 1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.2","name":"Esdras 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.36.23","name":"2 Chroniques 36:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.36.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.2","label":"","reference":"Esdras 1:2","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.001.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.001.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.1.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Ainsi parle Cyrus, roi des Perses: L\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu des cieux, m\u2019a donn\u00e9 tous les royaumes de la terre, et il m\u2019a command\u00e9 de lui b\u00e2tir une maison \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem en Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1","name":"Esdras 1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.3","name":"Esdras 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.1","name":"Esdras 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.3","label":"","reference":"Esdras 1:3","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.001.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.001.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.1.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Qui d\u2019entre vous est de son peuple? Que son Dieu soit avec lui, et qu\u2019il monte \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem en Juda et b\u00e2tisse la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl! C\u2019est le Dieu qui est \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1","name":"Esdras 1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.4","name":"Esdras 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.2","name":"Esdras 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.4","label":"","reference":"Esdras 1:4","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.001.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.001.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.1.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Dans tout lieu o\u00f9 s\u00e9journent des restes du peuple de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, les gens du lieu leur donneront de l\u2019argent, de l\u2019or, des effets, et du b\u00e9tail, avec des offrandes volontaires pour la maison de Dieu qui est \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1","name":"Esdras 1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.5","name":"Esdras 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.3","name":"Esdras 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.5","label":"","reference":"Esdras 1:5","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.001.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.001.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.1.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Les chefs de famille de Juda et de Benjamin, les sacrificateurs et les L\u00e9vites, tous ceux dont Dieu r\u00e9veilla l\u2019esprit, se lev\u00e8rent pour aller b\u00e2tir la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1","name":"Esdras 1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.6","name":"Esdras 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.4","name":"Esdras 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.6","label":"","reference":"Esdras 1:6","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.001.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.001.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.1.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Tous leurs alentours leur donn\u00e8rent des objets d\u2019argent, de l\u2019or, des effets, du b\u00e9tail, et des choses pr\u00e9cieuses, outre toutes les offrandes volontaires.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1","name":"Esdras 1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.7","name":"Esdras 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.5","name":"Esdras 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.7","label":"","reference":"Esdras 1:7","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.001.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.001.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.1.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Le roi Cyrus rendit les ustensiles de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, que Nebucadnetsar avait emport\u00e9s de J\u00e9rusalem et plac\u00e9s dans la maison de son dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1","name":"Esdras 1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.8","name":"Esdras 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.6","name":"Esdras 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.8","label":"","reference":"Esdras 1:8","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.001.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.001.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.1.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Cyrus, roi de Perse, les fit sortir par Mithredath, le tr\u00e9sorier, qui les remit \u00e0 Scheschbatsar, prince de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1","name":"Esdras 1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.9","name":"Esdras 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.7","name":"Esdras 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.9","label":"","reference":"Esdras 1:9","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.001.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.001.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.1.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>En voici le nombre: trente bassins d\u2019or, mille bassins d\u2019argent, vingt-neuf couteaux,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1","name":"Esdras 1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.10","name":"Esdras 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.8","name":"Esdras 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.10","label":"","reference":"Esdras 1:10","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.001.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.001.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.1.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>trente coupes d\u2019or, quatre cent dix coupes d\u2019argent de second ordre, mille autres ustensiles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1","name":"Esdras 1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.11","name":"Esdras 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.9","name":"Esdras 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.11","label":"","reference":"Esdras 1:11","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.001.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.002.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.1.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Tous les objets d\u2019or et d\u2019argent \u00e9taient au nombre de cinq mille quatre cents. Scheschbatsar emporta le tout de Babylone \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, au retour de la captivit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1","name":"Esdras 1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.2.1","name":"Esdras 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.2.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.1.10","name":"Esdras 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.1.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb9abe928.76030171');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb9abe928.76030171\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb9abe928.76030171","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb9abe928.76030171'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb9abe928.76030171\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"